<L>__{exterior plains country low angle shot day}
<A>__{a study of horseprints etched in the soil the mark of the passage of many horses; perhaps an eagle or turkey feather fallen from a warbonnet. and then we hear and see the approach of two plodding horses, and the dusty boots of the horsemen ethan and martin following the trail. the search theme resumes and continues over the next three shots, helping us suggest the passage of time, the change of scene.}
